<subSubSection pageId="6" pageNumber="64" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="6.[169,1383,276,1618]" pageId="6" pageNumber="64">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[174,530,1420,1453]" pageId="6" pageNumber="64">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Least Concern on The IUCN Red List. Ratanaworabhan’s Tailless Fruit Bat has a wide distribution and presumably large population and tolerates some habitat modification.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
